"use strict";(self.webpackChunkmineflayer_guide=self.webpackChunkmineflayer_guide||[]).push([[7307],{1882:o=>{o.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"activateBlock","metadata":{"permalink":"/mineflayer-guide/activateBlock","source":"@site/blog/04-29-2024-activateBlock/index.md","title":"activateBlock","description":"Targeting Blocks","date":"2024-04-30T02:49:34.000Z","tags":[{"label":"activateBlock","permalink":"/mineflayer-guide/tags/activate-block"},{"label":"button","permalink":"/mineflayer-guide/tags/button"},{"label":"door","permalink":"/mineflayer-guide/tags/door"},{"label":"trapdoor","permalink":"/mineflayer-guide/tags/trapdoor"}],"readingTime":0.675,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Pix3lPirat3","title":"Maintainer of Mineflayer Guide","url":"https://github.com/pix3lpirat3","imageURL":"https://github.com/pix3lpirat3.png","key":"pix3lpirat3"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"activateBlock","title":"activateBlock","authors":["pix3lpirat3"],"tags":["activateBlock","button","door","trapdoor"]},"unlisted":false},"content":"## Targeting Blocks\\nRemember to properly target your block, and catch if there is no found block.\\n\\nSingular Block:\\n```js\\nlet block = bot.findBlock({\\n  matching: bot.registry.blocksByName[\'oak_door\'].id,\\n  maxDistance: 5\\n})\\nif(!block) return console.log(\'There were no blocks found!\')\\n```\\n\\nMultiple Blocks:\\n```JS\\nlet blocks = bot.findBlocks({\\n  matching: bot.registry.blocksByName[\'oak_door\'].id,\\n  maxDistance: 5,\\n  count: 3\\n}).map(loc => bot.blockAt(loc)) // returns a [Vec3], map to [Block]\\nif(!blocks) return console.log(\'There were no blocks found!\')\\n```\\n\\nThen remember to **look at** the block if needed\\n```jS\\nawait bot.lookAt(block.position) // <-- and learn to use async/await\\nbot.activateBlock(block);\\n```\\n\\n## Using Doors / Trapdoors\\n\\n```js\\nlet block = bot.findBlock({\\n  matching: bot.registry.blocksByName[\'oak_door\'].id,\\n  maxDistance: 5\\n})\\nawait bot.lookAt(block.position)\\nbot.activateBlock(block);\\n```\\n\\n## Using Button\\n```js\\nlet block = bot.findBlock({\\n  matching: bot.registry.blocksByName[\'oak_button\'].id,\\n  maxDistance: 5\\n})\\nawait bot.lookAt(block.position) // <-- buttons have a funny position, block face too\\nbot.activateBlock(block);\\n```"}]}')}}]);